<hw>Strat`a*rith"me*try</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/
army + <?/ number + <ets>-metry</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Mil.)</fld> <def>The
art of drawing up an army, or any given number of men, in any
geometrical figure, or of estimating or expressing the number of men in
such a figure.</def>⟦br⟧
